raw.name: Vistara Beach Resort
raw.description:
Enter the hideaway water world of Vistara Beach Resort in between the emerald Arabian Sea and pristine backwater, filled with lush tropical greenery.
Laze in your over water rustic cottage fringed by turquoise lagoon & mesmerizing views. 
At Vistara Beach
